{"article_id":"Z8R1hhpE5uWeofDI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Obamacare remains the law of the land","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"after an unexpected failed , late night vote","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"on what 's being referred to as a `` skinny repeal '' of the law in the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"After seven years campaigning on a promise","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"to repeal","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"and replace Obamacare ,","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"Senate Republicans came up just one vote short","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"of approving a measure","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"to finally dismantle parts of the law .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"`` This is clearly a disappointing moment , ''","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"remarked Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"The measure was called `` skinny repeal ''","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"because it only got rid of key parts of Obamacare , not all of it .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"But it did n't offer a replacement plan .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Arizona Sen. John McCain , along with Sens . Lisa Murkowski of Alaska and Susan Collins of Maine , voted against their party .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"McCain said","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"he did n't vote for the measure","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"because it had no replacement for Obamacare .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"`` Skinny repeal fell short","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"because it fell short of our promise","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"to repeal & replace Obamacare with a meaningful reform , ''","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Skinny repeal fell short","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"because it fell short of our promise","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to repeal & replace Obamacare w/ meaningful reform","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"https : //t.co/tZISIvccOO","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"- John McCain","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"( @ SenJohnMcCain )","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"July 28 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Many Republican senators were not huge fans of the failed bill ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"but wanted to pass it","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and use it as a starting point","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"to work on the Obamacare repeal","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that could be amended and changed in conference with the House .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Following the vote ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , admitted on the floor","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Obamacare is n't perfect ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and in an emotional moment , asked his GOP colleagues to do","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"as McCain said earlier this week ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and return back to regular order","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and work with another .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"`` All of us were so inspired by the speech and the life of the senator from Arizona , ''","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"`` And he asked us to go back to regular order ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"to bring back the Senate","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that some of us","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"who have been here a while","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"remember . '' `` Maybe this can be a moment","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"when we start doing that , ''","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"he added .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"The bill 's defeat is a crushing blow to both Senate leadership and President Donald Trump .","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"Taking to Twitter ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"the president said","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"the GOP should just let Obamacare implode .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"`` 3 Republicans and 48 Democrats let the American people down , ''","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"the president tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` As I said from the beginning ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"let ObamaCare implode ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"then deal .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Watch ! '' 3 Republicans and 48 Democrats let the American people down .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"As I said from the beginning ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"let ObamaCare implode ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"then deal .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Watch !","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"July 28 , 2017","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"The White House is disappointed","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"Senate Republicans ca n't seem to unite","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"to help them achieve Trump 's campaign promise .","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"The administration wanted a policy victory","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"as it 's dealing with public infighting between chief of staff Reince Preibus and new Communications Director Anthony Scaramucci .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Scaramucci blasted Preibus in a profanity-laced interview in the New Yorker ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"calling him a `` paranoid schizophrenic . ''","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"And in a CNN interview Thursday , Sacaramucci said ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"`` The fish stinks from the head down , ''","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"`` I can tell you two fish","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that do n't stink ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"and that 's me and the president . ''","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"White House Press Secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders downplayed the situation ,","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"saying ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"`` This is just healthy competition . ''","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"`` This is a White House","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that has a lot of different perspectives","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"because the president hires the very best people , ''","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"she told reporters .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"`` They 're not always going to agree .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"There are going to be a lot of different ideas .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Unlike previous administrations , this is n't group think . ''","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"As for McCain ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"once the skinny bill failed ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"he called for the bill to go back to committee , hold hearings ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"and getting input from both Republicans and Democrats .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"But the future of any more measures on Obamacare is unclear .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":191,"left":0,"right":190,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":162,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":145,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":124,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":113,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":106,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":98,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":1,"right":97,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":103,"right":104,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":100,"right":102,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":4,"right":99,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":7,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":108,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":14,"relation"